Package: mueRelativeRisk
Title: Estimates the relative risk based on the ratio of median unbiased estimates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rickey", "Carter", email = "carter.rickey@mayo.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements an estimator for relative risk based on the median unbiased estimator. The relative risk estimator is well defined and performs satisfactorily for a wide range of data configurations. The method is published and available freely here: \url{https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2918902/}.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.3)
Imports: stats
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
